.banner-trees img {

}
.banner-trees img#hill-bg {
  width: 100%;

}
.banner-trees img#hill-1 {
  left: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  object-fit: contain;
}
.banner-trees img#hill-2 {

  object-fit: contain;
